{"tid":1543994,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"兒童事務委員會：希望警務人員仔細閱讀《兒童權利公約》","createTime":"2019-09-05T11:40:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T12:22:00.000Z","uid":212626,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"62eb8544a9b55d2321a16573498ff96c753d20f6","tid":1543994,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:40:43.000Z","msg":"兒童事務委員會發公開信，指最近修訂《逃犯條例》引發多宗衝突事件，有多人被捕及受傷。被捕人士當中最低年齡為12歲，而受傷送院者更包括嬰兒在內，信中提到，儘管政治層面的抗爭原應與兒童存有一段距離，但事態發展已令兒童直接或間接受到影響。一班兒童事務委員會全體非官方委員呼籲，家長及老師、警隊、示威者以及醫護人員各方注意採取任何行動之前，需以兒童利益為優先考慮，在不安之中更需要守護兒童。<br />\n...<br />\n另外，<span style=\"color: red;\">公開信中提到希望警務人員仔細閱讀《兒童權利公約》，履行保護兒童的責任</span>；稱警隊考慮以武力驅散示威者時，要時刻謹記在示威人群當中或附近極可能有兒童(甚至嬰兒)，並應作出相應措施，保證兒童安全。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">對於被捕兒童，《公約》第37及40條保障其獲得合理待遇，包括拘捕只作為最後手段、不受酷刑、不人道及有辱人格的對待</span>；<span style=\"color: red;\">當局須迅速直接告知罪名及通知其父母，並讓有關兒童與家人保持聯繫</span>。<br />\n<br />\n信中呼籲成年示威者時刻留意身邊的兒童，當遇到衝突時，盡力保護他們的人身安全，並協助其迅速撤離險境；而醫護人員在繁忙的工作之中，除了一如以往謹守崗位提供專業服務外，尤其要關注求助兒童的精神狀態，在治療身體創傷之時，亦給予適當的心靈慰藉及支援。<br />\n<br />\n公開信中又稱，不論立場，全社會都要明白沒有兒童，即沒有未來，「<span style=\"color: red;\">成年人今天所種的因，就是兒童明天所承受的果</span>」，懇請全社會都以兒童最佳利益為優先考量，避免兒童生活在不安恐懼之中。<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2445265/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2445265%2F&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=4ae3644a\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2445265/</a>"},{"pid":"d9080907bfd699c99b3a42eca178a69973ce2af2","tid":1543994,"uid":55597,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:44:15.000Z","msg":"所有話示威者係曱甴既人都犯晒法"},{"pid":"e5d7e3f8808707fb8d9774bc7e302754d288cd40","tid":1543994,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:45:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/05/104231_3a6ab00f3ec1c5387f321c23ffcf1893.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F05%2F104231_3a6ab00f3ec1c5387f321c23ffcf1893.jpg&h=7d68f7dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">必問：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有幾倍OT收，係咪仲要&quot;好合理要屌埋女示者&quot;咁辛苦？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>民主訴求，缺一不可；<br />\n<br />\n以眼還眼，鷹犬全鎖；<br />\n<br />\n有錯企定，即決勿拖！<br />\n<br />\n民主斬件，仲當我傻！<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，未贏收科？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</strong></span></span></span></span><br />\n<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">除非你係個班那埋護照旁身嘅扮民霸權，永續利益獨賣囉！！！</span></span></span></span></strong></strong>"},{"pid":"143c254a96c29fabff2767b49c3fadc5a22ce7ad","tid":1543994,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:45:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e60f277cf867b237112e0825abd3fd255bbea081","tid":1543994,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:49:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7af7dd78bc70e18a3c946f6459e2b6cbbef26d4c","tid":1543994,"uid":34787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:53:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2bb3e5fc1cc27fa126bf961f1f9ec8ae5ef28771","tid":1543994,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:54:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e750b55dcd421c0e12c0067640348ae9ad0abdc9","tid":1543994,"uid":236509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:57:05.000Z","msg":"「成年人今天所種的因，就是兒童明天所承受的果」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幼犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f762ed5218f6a44d74cf8a50b439708f2646d80b","tid":1543994,"uid":77803,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:02:43.000Z","msg":"佢就書都唔讀多本仲會睇你呢啲條約咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"843d0f7fde23e469fb8e6add57ad4c03114a3a73","tid":1543994,"uid":221265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f762ed5218f6a44d74cf8a50b439708f2646d80b","tid":1543994,"uid":77803,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:02:43.000Z","msg":"佢就書都唔讀多本仲會睇你呢啲條約咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:09:20.000Z","msg":"高層，保安局局長點會冇讀書？"},{"pid":"bd4c0e8e94b8830c7628e45531b3eb8cdabdf66a","tid":1543994,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"843d0f7fde23e469fb8e6add57ad4c03114a3a73","tid":1543994,"uid":221265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f762ed5218f6a44d74cf8a50b439708f2646d80b","tid":1543994,"uid":77803,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:02:43.000Z","msg":"佢就書都唔讀多本仲會睇你呢啲條約咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:09:20.000Z","msg":"高層，保安局局長點會冇讀書？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:19:27.000Z","msg":"上樑不正下樑歪"},{"pid":"28cfb1cc28115c4fd34dea8aefa8be5a90658de0","tid":1543994,"uid":34787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:22:00.000Z","msg":"推"}]}